ONES is enabled, delete only stamps deleted_at. Active reads/listing and same-path dedup do not filter deleted_at or remove active_memory_projection, so a deleted row can stay visible and can make a later identical save return unchanged instead of creating a live replacement.\",\"impact\":\"memory_delete can report success while the deleted record remains addressable/search-visible and blocks re-save until a separate purge path runs.\",\"recommendation\":\"On soft delete, remove the row from active_memory_projection and require active read/dedup paths to add deleted_at IS NULL; ensure re-save ignores tombstoned predecessors unless explicitly purging/recovering.\",\"finding_class\":\"data_integrity\",\"content_hash\":\"3bdd421740838f04a1153ea33c33bac56f71a2f64f4d59a00ead391eae567b27\",\"status\":\"active\",\"scopeProof\":\"Scope spec targets memory store/index/lifecycle code under mcp_server and write-path safety.\"}],\"traceabilityChecks\":{\"summary\":{\"required\":2,\"executed\":2,\"pass\":0,\"partial\":2,\"fail\":0,\"blocked\":0,\"notApplicable\":0,\"gatingFailures\":0},\"results\":[{\"protocol\":\"spec_code\",\"level\":\"core\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002/spec.md:7-14\"],\"notes\":\"Implementation spot-check covered the requested memory store/lifecycle surfaces but not the full broad scope in one iteration.\"},{\"protocol\":\"checklist_evidence\",\"level\":\"core\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"evidence\":[],\"notes\":\"No checklist.md exists in the scope folder; marked partial rather than pass.\"}]},\"newFindingsRatio\":0.5,\"durationMs\":0,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-18T05:50:43Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55r2-b-2-1781761339355-o7qylx\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\"}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":1,\"passed\":true,\"activeP0P1\":1